title: Diamond 4 Jungler looking for mid duo or team.
body:
Interested in having a partner to climb/duo with or a serious/semi-serious team who enjoys playing the game at a high level. Add 'Master Namer' ingame if youre interested :)

http://oce.op.gg/summoner/userName=master+namer

Im only interested in a duo/team that are actively looking to improve more then they are looking to win. Toxicity is a big negative for me too, im pretty chill and very positive but I am not looking to waste time on people who get toxic over a game or a loss or two.

replies.body: hello, I have a team i will be starting up for the new year called, Team Digital Fury, so far its very small, but we're looking for players like ourselves who wish to better at the game we love and one day be a official team for the OCE label. If you want to ask any questions about it feel free to add me in game -shouri.
